To clone a repository:
git clone https://github.com/robingreig/raspi-git

To add the changes to the Index:
git add <filename>
git add *

To commit the changes to the HEAD, but not the remote repository yet:
git commit -m "Commit Message"

Pushing the changes to the master:
git push origin master

To sync the master back to raspi
git pull

good website: rogerdudler.github.io/git-guide



